        "c_proven_results_thA3FA": {
          "type": "c-proven-results",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "tab1_title": "Is This Right for Me?",
            "tab2_title": "How to Use",
            "use_custom_tab1_text": true,
            "custom_tab1_text": "<p>Hot flashes. Low energy. Mood swings. Disruptive sleep. Menopause doesn’t just disrupt your day, it impacts your long-term health. Berkeley Life Menopause and Heart Health Support delivers daily, non-hormonal symptom relief while supporting what many women overlook during menopause: their heart. It is the smart place to start to feel relief today for resilience tomorrow.</p>",
            "usage_title": "How to Use",
            "usage_subtitle": "",
            "usage_text": "<p>Take 1 Nitrate Complex capsule and 1 Pollen Complex capsule together daily, with water after food. Do not exceed the recommended daily intake unless under the direction of your provider. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans. Made without most allergens (milk, eggs, fish, shellfish, tree nuts, peanuts, wheat, soy). Gluten and gelatin free.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
