        "item2_article": "news/modern-man-nitric-oxide-maurice-daher",
        "item2_source": "Maurice Daher on The Modern Man Podcast",
        "item3_rating": 5,
        "item3_text": "<p>Nitric Oxide support is critical for autoimmune patients. It maximizes diet and lifestyle changes through optimal circulation. Supporting Nitric Oxide ensures blood flow, improves circulation, and enhances the effectiveness of my entire protocol. I recommend adding Berkeley Life’s Nitric Oxide to your health journey.</p>",
        "item3_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Avatar_Image.webp",
        "item3_name": "Dr. Terry Wahls",
        "item4_rating": 5,
        "item4_text": "<p>We saw a noticeable benefit when adding the Berkeley Life capsules into our procedures. Blood flow and healing are critical to the success of our treatments, and the integration of Nitric Oxide has really helped. We continue to promote Berkeley’s N.O. because our patients are loving the results.</p>",
        "item4_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/icon-doctor-1.webp",
        "item4_name": "Dr. Richard Moore",
        "item5_article": "news/what-nitric-oxide-does-for-your-body-circulation-energy-sexual-health-cathy-eason-on-age-like-a-badass-mother-podcast",
        "item5_source": "Cathy Eason on Age Like a Badass Mother Podcast",
        "item6_article": "news/blood-flow-wellness-nitric-oxide",
        "item6_source": "Why Circulation is the New Marker of Wellness",
        "item7_article": "news/nitric-oxide-healthy-aging-cathy-eason",
        "item7_source": "Cathy Eason on the Aging Well Podcast",
        "item8_rating": 5,
        "item8_text": "<p>Berkeley Life is a company that has gained my respect for their commitment to the development of science-based products that modulate Nitric Oxide status and function. Their commitment to scientific rigor and innovative solutions makes them a powerful ally in the pursuit of functional health.</p>",
        "item8_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Avatar_Image_1.webp",
        "item8_name": "Dr. Jeffrey Bland"
      }
    },
