            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "How does Nitric Oxide support women during menopause?",
            "answer": "<p>As estrogen levels decline as your naturally age, your body’s natural Nitric Oxide production also drops which may affect circulation and energy. Supporting  healthy Nitric Oxide production helps promotes optimal blood flow and vitality.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_yibBh7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "Is this product hormone-free?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. This formula is 100%  hormone free. It can also be used alongside HRT under supervision of your healthcare provider.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_PpyqdR": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "How does it support heart health?",
            "answer": "<p>Estrogen levels naturally decline with age which can affect circulation and cardiovascular function. The Nitric Oxide Support capsules support blood vessel relaxation, healthy circulation and cardiovascular function for overall well-being during menopause and beyond </p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_brpzHQ": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "How do I take it?",
            "answer": "<p>Take two capsules daily—one Nitrate Complex capsule and one Pollen Complex capsule—with water after food. Consistency is key for optimal results and sustained Nitric Oxide support.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_W4qiXp": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "med-2",
            "question": "Can I take this with other supplements or medications?",
            "answer": "<p>As with any new supplement, it’s best to discuss it with your healthcare provider.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_WnFcqr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "fp",
            "question": "Who can become a Berkeley Life provider or partner?",
            "answer": "<p>Berkeley Life partners with licensed healthcare providers and qualified clinical professionals, including physicians, dentists, nurse practitioners, chiropractors, and integrative or functional medicine practitioners. Our program supports providers who want to incorporate Nitric Oxide education, products, and testing into evidence-based patient care.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_PbemgP": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "fp",
            "question": "Is there wholesale pricing available?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Verified Berkeley Life providers receive access to exclusive wholesale pricing for in-practice use and patient dispensing. Wholesale accounts also include access to provider-only resources, education, and support to help integrate Berkeley Life products into clinic or practice.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_F96iRM": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "fp",
            "question": "What resources does Berkeley Life provide for clinicians?",
            "answer": "<p>Verified providers receive access to wholesale pricing, patient education materials, clinical insights, and select marketing support to help confidently introduce Berkeley Life within their practice.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_rYaA7T": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "fp",
            "question": "How do providers log in to their Berkeley Life account?",
            "answer": "<p>Once approved, providers can log in through the <strong>Provider Login</strong> link on the Berkeley Life website using the email address associated with their application. If you experience login issues, our support team is available to assist.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_rGMGUP": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "fp",
            "question": "How long does it take to become a verified provider?",
            "answer": "<p>Most provider applications are reviewed and verified within 1–2 business days. Once approved, you’ll receive confirmation and login credentials to access provider-only pricing and resources.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_xcBFPr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "safety",
            "question": "Is Berkeley Life safe for daily use?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Berkeley Life is manufactured in the United States under FDA-registered, GMP-certified facilities, and undergoes rigorous internal and third-party testing to ensure safety and potency.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_DeG7X4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "safety",
            "question": "What quality standards do you follow?",
            "answer": "<p>Every ingredient is tested for identity, potency, and microbiological safety before use. Finished products undergo comprehensive quality checks and third-party testing before being released.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_QctQnH": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "safety",
            "question": "Can I validate that Berkeley Life is working for me?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. You can use the Nitric Oxide Test Strips before and 90 minutes after taking the supplement to confirm effectiveness.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_QjPgkr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "safety",
            "question": "Where is Berkeley Life made?",
            "answer": "<p>Supplements are manufactured in the USA, and test strips are produced in Europe.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_aNRGdk": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
