            "question": "How much should I take daily?",
            "answer": "<p>Take two capsules daily with water, preferably after a meal.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_gCKxeV": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "dosage",
            "question": "How long do I need to take Berkeley Life before I see results?",
            "answer": "<p>Results vary, some notice a difference right away, while others see benefits after about a month. Consistency is key, and test strips can validate improvements quickly.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_KAmrV7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "dosage",
            "question": "How long should I continue taking Nitric Oxide support?",
            "answer": "<p>Since natural nitric oxide production declines with age, ongoing daily support through diet or supplementation is recommended.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_CCyhPB": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "dosage",
            "question": "What if my test strip doesn’t change color?",
            "answer": "<p>If you recently ate or drank, saliva may be diluted, causing a false negative. In rare cases, low oral bacteria levels may impact conversion. We recommend discussing ways to support your oral microbiome with your healthcare provider.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
